description:
Authors:  Alexei Uteshev (St Petersbourg) et Piet Bikker (Linz).

The aim was to find eliminant in $t$ - it will be A HUGE poly
of the degree 36 with the coefficients of the  order 10^{50}.
As I've told you it was constructed with the aim of checking an
exceptional case in Bezout's method.
